      "text": "むむ……予定では95点は堅いはずだったのに……\n歌手でも採点で100点取りにくい説は本当でしたか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… I was sure I'd get at least 95 points…\nSo it's true that even professional singers rarely get 100 points!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8250797431,
      "sfxList": []
