      "text": "ミクはさすが、バーチャル・シンガーだな……\n一度聴いただけで、ここまで正確に合わせられるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku really is amazing as a virtual singer…\nTo match so accurately after hearing it just once",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3283425809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
