      "text": "いいね、楽しそう。次は僕もミクと一緒に歌おうかな\n『Blue sky summer』辺りを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice‚ looks fun. Maybe I'll sing with Miku next\nSomething like \"Blue sky summer\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
