      "text": "あー、葵さんズルいです！\nじゃあ私も『最高優美ロンリネス』を入れます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah―‚ Aoi‚ that's not fair!\nThen I'll put in \"Saikou Yubi Loneliness\" too!",
