      "text": "きゅ……98点！？\nしかも、初めてのデュエットなのに……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ni… 98 points!?\nAnd it's your first duet together…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8594077033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
