      "text": "（その後も大いに盛り上がったが）\n（さすがに疲れが出てしまったんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Things continued to be lively after that）\n（But fatigue seemed to set in）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9269183319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さんとミク以外は、早々に脱落）\n（俺達は三人で、まったりとした時間を過ごした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Everyone except Rio and Miku left early）\n（The three of us spent a relaxed time together）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2269183319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9758852883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
