      "text": "改めてにはなるけど……ミク\n今回はライブに出演してくれて、本当にありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know I'm repeating myself‚ but… Miku\nThank you so much for performing at our live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
