      "text": "北海道公演だからこそのサプライズとして\n最高に盛り上がったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a surprise special to our Hokkaido performance\nIt was the most exciting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "アンコールだけだったのが、もったいないぐらい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To the point where it's a shame it was only for the encore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2035433058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-ymk003.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ。北海道の冬を盛り上げるために\nいろいろ考えて、協力してくれて、凄く嬉しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too. To make Hokkaido's winter more exciting\nIt made me so happy that you thought of everything and cooperated",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ミクが登場した時のみんなの反応\n本当に凄かったわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's reaction when Miku appeared\nWas really amazing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ嬉しいサプライズになったということかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess it means it was that much of a happy surprise",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9395450833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-ymk004.m4a",
      "text": "かもしれないね。嬉しかったなぁ\nもっと共演していたかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe so. I was happy\nI wish we could have performed together more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.4666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そうよね\n楽しい時間って、本当にあっという間……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know\nFun times really do fly by…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.233333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.5828023513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いずれまた、共演する機会もありますよ\n今回みたいな偶然があったぐらいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There will be opportunities to perform together again someday\nSince we had a chance like this by coincidence",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.5935880502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.3659063581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあその時は、今日以上に大々的な\nイベントを企画してくれる……ってことでいいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then next time‚ something even grander\nWill you plan an event for us…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.5602547169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "う……確約は出来ないけど……分かりました\n最大限、努力します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… I can't promise‚ but… alright\nI'll do my best",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.2269213836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.1598518931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
