      "text": "はぁ……けど、本当に寂しいわね\nもう明後日には東京に帰るだなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… but it's really sad\nTo think we're going back to Tokyo the day after tomorrow",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.1269193491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "明日はオフだし、ゆっくり観光でもどうです？\nといっても、札幌市内はあらかた回っちゃいましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow's our day off‚ how about some sightseeing?\nAlthough we've already seen most of Sapporo city",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.4602526825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
