      "text": "……じゃあ、私が直接\n北海道を案内してもいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Then‚ how about I\nGuide you around Hokkaido?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.9666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "え……いいのか？\nミクにも自分の仕事があるんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… is that okay?\nDon't you have your own work to do‚ Miku?",
        "id": ""
      },
