      "text": "ありがとう、ミク……！\nせっかくだし、お願いしようかしら。いいわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Miku…!\nSince we have the chance‚ shall we take her up on it? Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.8269264699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
