      "text": "……北海道って、本当に広いのね\n私、ちょっと舐めていたかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hokkaido is really vast\nI might have underestimated it a bit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.0269498667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
