      "text": "同じ道内だから、近いと思ってたけど\n特急列車で三時間もかかるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it would be close since it's within the same prefecture\nTo think it takes three hours by express train",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.6116211141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "北海道旅行の初心者あるあるだなぁ……\n広過ぎて距離感間違えるやつ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a common mistake for first―time Hokkaido travelers…\nMisjudging distances because it's so vast…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.3602832001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
